    <title>UOS、Deepin安装必备</title>
    <link href="/2024/01/07/Linux%E8%A3%85%E6%9C%BA%E5%BF%85%E5%A4%87/"/>
    <url>/2024/01/07/Linux%E8%A3%85%E6%9C%BA%E5%BF%85%E5%A4%87/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p> 本文档在使用Linux系统所写，旨在方便Linux环境的安装。主要适用于国产UOS和Deepin系统。</p></blockquote><h2 id="一、APT换源"><a href="#一、APT换源" class="headerlink" title="一、APT换源"></a>一、APT换源</h2><h3 id="1、保存源文件"><a href="#1、保存源文件" class="headerlink" title="1、保存源文件"></a>1、保存源文件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">cp</span> -r /etc/apt/sources.list /etc/apt/sources.list.bak</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、更换源"><a href="#2、更换源" class="headerlink" title="2、更换源"></a>2、更换源</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-security main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-security main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-updates main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-updates main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-proposed main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-proposed main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-backports main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ bionic-backports main restricted universe multiverse</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3、添加公钥"><a href="#3、添加公钥" class="headerlink" title="3、添加公钥"></a>3、添加公钥</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-key adv --recv-keys --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.com 40976EAF437D05B5 3B4FE6ACC0B21F32</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4、更新"><a href="#4、更新" class="headerlink" title="4、更新"></a>4、更新</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5、更新公钥"><a href="#5、更新公钥" class="headerlink" title="5、更新公钥"></a>5、更新公钥</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-key adv --refresh-keys --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6、常见问题"><a href="#6、常见问题" class="headerlink" title="6、常见问题"></a>6、常见问题</h3><p>由于出现了 “invalid packet” 的错误消息，可能是由于密钥文件本身的问题导致的。建议您尝试使用以下方法来解决该问题：</p><ol><li><p>删除 <code>/etc/apt/trusted.gpg</code> 文件：</p><p>sudo rm &#x2F;etc&#x2F;apt&#x2F;trusted.gpg</p></li><li><p>创建一个新的空白 <code>trusted.gpg</code> 文件：</p><p>sudo touch &#x2F;etc&#x2F;apt&#x2F;trusted.gpg</p></li><li><p>导入密钥：</p><p>sudo apt-key adv –keyserver <a href="http://keyserver.ubuntu.com/">keyserver.ubuntu.com</a> –recv-keys <KEY></p><p>注意，将 <code>&lt;KEY&gt;</code> 替换为您要导入的密钥的指纹。</p></li><li><p>重复步骤3，为每个要导入的密钥重复该步骤。</p></li></ol><h2 id="二、Linux安装MySQL8"><a href="#二、Linux安装MySQL8" class="headerlink" title="二、Linux安装MySQL8"></a>二、Linux安装MySQL8</h2><h3 id="1、下载apt安装源"><a href="#1、下载apt安装源" class="headerlink" title="1、下载apt安装源"></a>1、下载apt安装源</h3><p>从MySQL官网下载apt安装包： <a href="https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/repo/apt/">https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/repo/apt/</a></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/98j5cMqxP1lAkfW.png" alt="img"></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/k4uHMUagzfyCp6m.png" alt="img"></p><p>下载成功得到这样一个文件：</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/QdnTgavOGz2cJ1A.png" alt="img"></p><h3 id="2、安装MySQL8-x"><a href="#2、安装MySQL8-x" class="headerlink" title="2、安装MySQL8.x"></a>2、安装MySQL8.x</h3><p>安装已下载的deb包</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/pn1wEVHSWjAae9m.png" alt="img"></p><p>即出现黄色界面，因为deepinV20是基于Debian10,因此我们选择第三项”Debian buster“</p><p>然后选择确认</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/xYGikDSMTEZN19s.png" alt="img"></p><p>确认后出现版本选择界面，选择第一项，并确认</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/RJVi1p4YEGN7fwt.png" alt="img"></p><p>选择8.0,再次确认即可</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/kuZoUdclefPQGMD.png" alt="选择版本"></p><p>确认之后会返回该界面，不要怀疑，没有错。</p><p>这次选择OK，和确认。</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/VLiIzCYr3hAStgF.png" alt="img"></p><p>确认后会出现警告报错。不用担心，看下一步。</p><p>执行如下命令：sudo apt-get update  如果出现某个连接超时，重新执行该命令重试即可。）</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/qQanK1dTHJb3XDE.png" alt="img"></p><p>接下来执行：<code>sudo apt-get install mysql-server</code></p><p>选择【Y&#x2F;N】输入Y</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/bynxp9d8gJZA7eM.png" alt="img"></p><p>如果不报错，请略过这一步</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/5gwInrPjoRXp2zB.png" alt="img"></p><p>如果出现这样的报错，执行：sudo apt-get update –fix-missing</p><p>完成后，再次执行：sudo apt-get install mysql-server</p><p>同样选择Y。</p><p>等待下载</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/uJD1WXAemPblaV9.png" alt="开始安装"></p><p>再次出现黄色界面时，说明成功一半了。</p><p>输入root 密码 确认</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/IizCV7ZOyaESem5.png" alt="输入密码"></p><p>再次输入密码 确认</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/GEtYTMQHokil6yf.png" alt="img"></p><p>点击退出即可</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/PNbJyVgljT37sWz.png" alt="img"></p><p>点击确认即可</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/4ypaAhxFtUnO8Yf.png" alt="img"></p><p>等待安装即可</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/Qo85thlfGS1Ha3e.png" alt="img"></p><p>到这说明安装完了</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/Ly5Z2b8qPnlj7sY.png" alt="img"></p><p>确认下MySQL服务器版本，执行：<code>apt policy mysql-server </code></p><p>大功快告成！</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/Zz1s4drSQvIY2WC.png" alt="确认版本"></p><p>启动MySQL服务，执行：<code>sudo systemctl start mysql  </code></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/Gq2M3Z58tRedcan.png" alt="img"></p><p>再执行进入命令：mysql -u root -p</p><p>输入密码</p><p>这个就不用说了吧：show databases;</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/M2jeLBYowRTKECD.png" alt="安装成功"></p><h2 id="三、Linux安装Node和Npm"><a href="#三、Linux安装Node和Npm" class="headerlink" title="三、Linux安装Node和Npm"></a>三、Linux安装Node和Npm</h2><h3 id="1、先安装Node"><a href="#1、先安装Node" class="headerlink" title="1、先安装Node"></a>1、先安装Node</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt update // 更新安装库</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install nodejs // 安装nodejs</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install npm // 安装npm</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">npm install -g n // 安装node版本管理工具</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">npm install -g yarn // 安装yarn，如果有需要用到的话</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、更新npm时可能发生错误"><a href="#2、更新npm时可能发生错误" class="headerlink" title="2、更新npm时可能发生错误"></a>2、更新npm时可能发生错误</h3><p>安装后的node版本为10.24.0，npm的版本为5.8.0</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm WARN npm npm does not support Node.js v10.24.0</span><br><span class="line">npm WARN npm You should probably upgrade to a newer version of node as we</span><br><span class="line">npm WARN npm can<span class="string">&#x27;t make any promises that npm will work with this version.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">**npm WARN npm Supported releases of Node.js are the latest release of 4, 6, 7, 8, 9.**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">npm WARN npm You can find the latest version at https://nodejs.org/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">npm WARN checkPermissions Missing write access to /usr/local/lib/node_modules</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">npm ERR! path /usr/local/lib/node_modules</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">npm ERR! code EACCES</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">……</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3、解决方案"><a href="#3、解决方案" class="headerlink" title="3、解决方案"></a>3、解决方案</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 重新下载nodejs 注意重新下载的以4，6，7，8，9结尾</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 链接：https://nodejs.org/dist/v18.18.0/node-v18.18.0-linux-x64.tar.xz</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo apt remove nodejs</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将解压的安装包放在指定位置，并进行系统配置</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo vim /etc/profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/91XKLCkxYTO4HBJ.png" alt="img"></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 使得配置文件生效</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">source</span> /etc/profile /etc/bash.bashrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这时查看node和npm的版本号</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/MAt8YvZgsEjoQip.png" alt="img"></p><h3 id="4、继续更新"><a href="#4、继续更新" class="headerlink" title="4、继续更新"></a>4、继续更新</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g n</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/zLYlSh3u1PMAgHO.png" alt="img"></p><p>有需要可以再安装个<strong>yarn</strong></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/Duzvp1T8kJxyPLe.png" alt="img"></p><h2 id="四、Linux安装Redis"><a href="#四、Linux安装Redis" class="headerlink" title="四、Linux安装Redis"></a>四、Linux安装Redis</h2><h3 id="1、下载Redis"><a href="#1、下载Redis" class="headerlink" title="1、下载Redis"></a>1、下载Redis</h3><p><a href="https://redis.io/download/**%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDRedis%E4%BA%8C%E8%BF%9B%E5%88%B6%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6">https://redis.io/download/**下载Redis二进制文件</a>**</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/etDjyHJM2If3cQF.png" alt="img"></p><h3 id="2、安装Redis"><a href="#2、安装Redis" class="headerlink" title="2、安装Redis"></a>2、安装Redis</h3><h4 id="2-1-解压缩包"><a href="#2-1-解压缩包" class="headerlink" title="2.1 解压缩包"></a>2.1 解压缩包</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -zxvf redis-7.2.1-tar-xz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/aBmQcXpZ4iySu3w.png" alt="img"></p><h4 id="2-2-打开终端"><a href="#2-2-打开终端" class="headerlink" title="2.2 打开终端"></a>2.2 打开终端</h4><p>输入<strong>make</strong>指令进行安装，直到显示下图表示安装成功</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/H4kVJWXBZ2u19q7.png" alt="img"></p><h4 id="2-3-测试服务"><a href="#2-3-测试服务" class="headerlink" title="2.3 测试服务"></a>2.3 测试服务</h4><p>进入src目录，打开<strong>redis-server</strong>服务</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> src/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/k4rVSxNPgJEw3ny.png" alt="img"></p><p>新建窗口，客户端测试功能</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/6Q4zVHrBTk8fM3b.png" alt="img"></p><h3 id="3、配置Redis环境"><a href="#3、配置Redis环境" class="headerlink" title="3、配置Redis环境"></a>3、配置Redis环境</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">## Redis</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> REDIS_HOME=/home/awk/Resourses/redis-7.2.1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">export</span> PATH=<span class="variable">$PATH</span>:<span class="variable">$REDIS_HOME</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 自定义指令</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /persistent/home/awk/Items/redis-7.2.2/src &amp;&amp; ./redis-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/8YgZX4mUNFREADJ.png" alt="img"></p><h2 id="五、Linux安装python3-x"><a href="#五、Linux安装python3-x" class="headerlink" title="五、Linux安装python3.x"></a>五、Linux安装python3.x</h2><h3 id="1、安装前的准备"><a href="#1、安装前的准备" class="headerlink" title="1、安装前的准备"></a>1、安装前的准备</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt upgrade</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、安装必须的依赖"><a href="#2、安装必须的依赖" class="headerlink" title="2、安装必须的依赖"></a>2、安装必须的依赖</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install make build-essential libssl-dev zlib1g-dev</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install libbz2-dev libreadline-dev libsqlite3-dev wget curl llvm</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install libncurses5-dev libncursesw5-dev xz-utils tk-dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3、下载安装包"><a href="#3、下载安装包" class="headerlink" title="3、下载安装包"></a>3、下载安装包</h3><blockquote><p>可以放在任意位置，我在数据盘的&#x2F;home&#x2F;awk&#x2F;Items下编译的</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /home/awk/Items</span><br><span class="line">sudo wget https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.10.6/Python-3.10.6.tgz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果wget网速太慢或者下载不了，可以直接将 <a href="https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.10.6/Python-3.10.6.tgz">https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.10.6/Python-3.10.6.tgz</a> 粘贴到网页地址栏中下载即可。</p><h3 id="4、解压并开始编译"><a href="#4、解压并开始编译" class="headerlink" title="4、解压并开始编译"></a>4、解压并开始编译</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo tar -zxvf Python-3.10.6tgz</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> Python-3.10.</span><br><span class="line">sudo ./configure prefix=/usr/local/python3 --with-openssl=/usr  --with-http_ssl_module  --enable-optimizations</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo make </span><br><span class="line">sudo make install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>注：将python的环境编译到&#x2F;usr&#x2F;bin&#x2F;python3的目录下，默认和python2一个目录下；如需编译到指定自定义目录，可添加 –prefix&#x3D;&#x2F;usr&#x2F;local&#x2F;python3指定</li></ul><h3 id="5、创建软链接"><a href="#5、创建软链接" class="headerlink" title="5、创建软链接"></a>5、创建软链接</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">ln</span> -s /usr/local/python3/bin/python3 /usr/bin/python</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果创建链接失败，可以采取以下两种办法重试</p><ul><li>1.使用unlink取消链接，再重新创建链接</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">unlink</span> python3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>2.将原有的链接先备份，再创建自己想要的链接</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">mv</span> /usr/bin/python3 /usr/bin/python3_backup</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6、配置pip"><a href="#6、配置pip" class="headerlink" title="6、配置pip"></a>6、配置pip</h3><p>在安装完Python3.x也会将pip安装成功，进入目录并给pip3.x创建软链接即可</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">ln</span> -s /usr/local/python3/bin/pip3.10 /usr/bin/pip3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>pip设置加速</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip config <span class="built_in">set</span> global.index-url https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple</span><br><span class="line">pip config <span class="built_in">set</span> install.trusted-host mirrors.aliyun.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="附录：pip国内镜像源"><a href="#附录：pip国内镜像源" class="headerlink" title="附录：pip国内镜像源"></a>附录：pip国内镜像源</h3><figure class="highlight text"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip国内镜像源：</span><br><span class="line">阿里云——http://mirrors.aliyun.com/pypi/simple/</span><br><span class="line">中国科技大学——https://pypi.mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/simple/</span><br><span class="line">豆瓣————http://pypi.douban.com/simple</span><br><span class="line">Python官方——https://pypi.python.org/simple/</span><br><span class="line">v2ex——http://pypi.v2ex.com/simple/</span><br><span class="line">中国科学院——http://pypi.mirrors.opencas.cn/simple/</span><br><span class="line">清华大学——https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="六、UOS更新错误问题处理"><a href="#六、UOS更新错误问题处理" class="headerlink" title="六、UOS更新错误问题处理"></a>六、UOS更新错误问题处理</h2><p>今天更新源之后，想查看一下有没有要更新的东西，顺便都更新完成了，可是发生了接下来的事情：</p><h3 id="1、更新"><a href="#1、更新" class="headerlink" title="1、更新"></a>1、更新</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt upgrade</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>结果：</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">有一些软件包无法被安装。如果您用的是 unstable 发行版，这也许是</span><br><span class="line">因为系统无法达到您要求的状态造成的。该版本中可能会有一些您需要的软件</span><br><span class="line">包尚未被创建或是它们已被从新到(Incoming)目录移出。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/FRxp7Z2vqJdhNDz.png" alt="img"></p><hr><h3 id="2、解决方案"><a href="#2、解决方案" class="headerlink" title="2、解决方案"></a>2、解决方案</h3><ul><li>安装aptitude</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install aptitude</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>安装正要被安装的软件包 libsensors4，输入“Y”</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo aptitude install libsensors4</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>继续更新，输入“Y”继续</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt upgrade</span><br><span class="line">在更新的时候报错了：</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/WGN2tMfP5ERa7Im.png" alt="错误提示"></p><ul><li>刷新后继续更新</li></ul><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt upgrade</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>继续修改错误，安装软件包  <strong>libgstreamer-plugins-good1.0-0</strong></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/fj6yzSFs2vGnhLp.png" alt="img"></p><p><strong>会出现一个UI框，可以上下进行选择，直接选择最后一项</strong></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/psZcUPdk9WQ42rY.png" alt="img"></p><p><strong>安装软件包</strong></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/zu7SxsEoGm143Hk.png" alt="img"></p><p><strong>最后完成的截图</strong></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/mhj6oQ3qEYDBfkF.png" alt="img"></p></li></ul><h3 id="3、最终测试"><a href="#3、最终测试" class="headerlink" title="3、最终测试"></a>3、最终测试</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt upgrade</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2024/01/07/nibOFqv1rCsjZmK.png" alt="img"></p><h2 id="七、Linux安装和卸载docker"><a href="#七、Linux安装和卸载docker" class="headerlink" title="七、Linux安装和卸载docker"></a>七、Linux安装和卸载docker</h2><h3 id="1-安装docker"><a href="#1-安装docker" class="headerlink" title="1. 安装docker"></a>1. 安装docker</h3><p>1.1 首先，更新软件包索引，并且安装必要的依赖软件，来添加一个新的 HTTPS 软件源：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install apt-transport-https ca-certificates curl gnupg-agent software-properties-common</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>1.2 使用下面的 curl 导入源仓库的 GPG key</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/ubuntu/gpg | sudo apt-key add -</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>1.3 将 Docker APT 软件源添加到你的系统</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo add-apt-repository <span class="string">&quot;deb [arch=amd64] https://download.docker.ucom/linux/ubuntu <span class="subst">$(lsb_release -cs)</span> stable&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>1.4 Docker 软件源被启用了，你可以安装软件源中任何可用的 Docker 版本</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 直接安装新版本</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 想要安装指定版本，首先列出docker软件源所有可用的版本</span></span><br><span class="line">apt list -a docker-ce</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install docker-ce=&lt;VERSION&gt; docker-ce-cli=&lt;VERSION&gt; containerd.io</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>1.5 一旦安装完成，Docker 服务将会自动启动。你可以输入下面的命令，验证它</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl status docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出将会类似下面这样：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root@awk-virtual-machine:~<span class="comment"># sudo systemctl status docker</span></span><br><span class="line">● docker.service - Docker Application Container Engine</span><br><span class="line">     Loaded: loaded (/lib/systemd/system/docker.service; enabled; vendor preset: enabled)</span><br><span class="line">     Active: active (running) since Thu 2022-05-05 17:19:56 CST; 18s ago</span><br><span class="line">TriggeredBy: ● docker.socket</span><br><span class="line">       Docs: https://docs.docker.com</span><br><span class="line">   Main PID: 3668 (dockerd)</span><br><span class="line">      Tasks: 9</span><br><span class="line">     Memory: 37.9M</span><br><span class="line">     CGroup: /system.slice/docker.service</span><br><span class="line">             └─3668 /usr/bin/dockerd -H fd:// --containerd=/run/containerd/containerd.sock</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当一个新的 Docker 发布时，你可以使用标准的 sudo apt update &amp;&amp; sudo apt upgrade 来升级 Docker 软件包。</p><p>1.6 如果你想阻止 Docker 自动更新，锁住它的版本</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-mark hold docker-ce</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>1.7 以非 Root 用户身份执行 Docker</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># PS: $USER指的是当前系统的用户名</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo usermod -aG docker <span class="variable">$USER</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo groupadd docker     <span class="comment">#添加docker用户组</span></span><br><span class="line">sudo gpasswd -a <span class="variable">$USER</span> docker     <span class="comment">#将登陆用户加入到docker用户组中</span></span><br><span class="line">newgrp docker     <span class="comment">#更新用户组</span></span><br><span class="line">docker ps    <span class="comment">#测试docker命令是否可以使用sudo正常使用</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-卸载docker"><a href="#2-卸载docker" class="headerlink" title="2. 卸载docker"></a>2. 卸载docker</h3><p>2.1 删除某软件,及其安装时自动安装的所有包</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get autoremove docker docker-ce docker-engine  docker.io  containerd runc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.2 查看删除<a href="https://so.csdn.net/so/search?q=docker&spm=1001.2101.3001.7020">docker</a>其他有没有没有卸载干净的包</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">dpkg -l | grep docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.3 卸载相应的包</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get autoremove docker-ce-*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.4 删除docker的相关配置&amp;目录</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">rm</span> -rf /etc/systemd/system/docker.service.d</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo <span class="built_in">rm</span> -rf /var/lib/docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.5 确定docker卸载完毕</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
